&lt;li&gt;Oversee task order implementation, including scope confirmation, resource planning, schedule tracking, deliverable tracking, risk management, reporting, and closeout support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate across technical leadership, and corporate functions to ensure execution is aligned, dependencies are visible, and blockers are resolved quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
